ainment in 2013 and began recording new music in 2014.<ref name=IMDb3>{{cite web |url = https://www.imdb.com/company/co0490137/ |title = Urban Genius Entertainment |publisher = IMDb |accessdate = 21 March 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Private life==\n\nMarquis is married and has three daughters. He currently lives and works in [[Los Angeles]].<ref name=Purple>{{cite web |url = http://purplebars.com/spotlight-interview-jaron-marquis/ |title = Spotlight Interview: Jaron Marquis |publisher = Purple Bars |author = Trish Wallace |date = 24 September 2016 |accessdate = 21 March 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Singles===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!align=\"left\"|Year\n!align=\"left\"|Title<ref name=iTunes>{{cite web |url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/jaron-marquis/id1148686809 |title = Jaron Marquis |publisher = iTunes |accessdate = 21 March 2017}}</ref>\n!align=\"left\"|Label\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2016\n|Applause\n|rowspan=\"3\"|Urban Genius Entertainment\n|-\n|Baby Yeah\n|-\n|2017\n|That's My N***a\n|-\n|}\n\n===Mixtapes===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!align=\"left\"|Year\n!align=\"left\"|Title\n|-\n|2014\n|''Soul of a Genius''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"margin-right: 0;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title<ref name=IMDb>{{cite web |url = https://www.imdb.com/name/nm6210967/ |title = Jaron Marquis Garrett |publisher = IMDb |accessdate = 21 March 2017}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''Girl Crazy''\n| Bobby\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''Antihero''\n| Stranger\n| short\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2015\n| ''[[HitRecord on TV]]''\n| himself\n| also: composer and musician\n|-\n| ''[[Furious 7]]''\n| L.A. Street Racer\n| uncredited\n|-\n| ''[[Straight Outta Compton (film)|Straight Outta Compton]]''\n| T-shirt vendor\n| uncredited\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|3}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://jaronmarquis.com/}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT