icdefencereporter.com\"/>\n|Tracked SAM system\n|-\n| [[File:IGLA-S_MANPADS_at_IDELF-2008.jpg|120px]]||[[9K38 Igla]] (SA-18 Grouse)&(SA-16)\n| {{Flagu|USSR}}\n| 100 x SA16<ref name=\"armstrade.sipri.org\"/><br> 400 x SA18<ref name=\"asiapacificdefencereporter.com\"/>\n| Very short-range portable surface-to-air missile system ([[MANPADS]])\n|-\n| [[File:Hwasong 6.jpg|20px]]||[[Hwasong-6]]\n| {{Flagu|North Korea}}\n| 11<ref>[[Hwasong-6#Operators]]</ref>{{verification needed|date=September 2019}}\n| [[Scud]] missile with range:700&nbsp;km\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | '''[[Anti-aircraft gun|Gun systems]]'''\n|-\n|[[File:61-K.jpg|120px]]||[[37 mm automatic air defense gun M1939 (61-K)|Type-74]]\n| {{Flagu|USSR}}\n| 24<ref name=\"armstrade.sipri.org\"/>\n| 37&nbsp;mm\n|-\n|[[File:QF 40mm Mk1 CFB Borden 1.jpg|120px]]|| [[Anti-Aircraft Guns]] Various model\n| Various\n|200<ref name=\"asiapacificdefencereporter.com\"/>\n|37mm/40mm/57mm Anti-Aircraft Guns\n|-\n|[[File:14,5-\u043c\u043c \u0441\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0437\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0442\u043d\u0430\u044f \u043f\u0443\u043b\u0435\u043c\u0435\u0442\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0443\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u043a\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0443\u043a\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u041b\u0435\u0449\u0438\u043d\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0417\u041f\u0423-4 (4).jpg|120px]]||[[KPV heavy machine gun]]\n| {{Flagu|USSR}}\n|\n|\n|}\n \n===Anti Tank===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n! width=\"10%\"| Photo\n! Model\n! Origin\n! Quantity\n! Notes\n|-\n! style=\"background:lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | Systems\n|-\n|[[File:Rcl106lat2.jpg|120px]]||[[M40 recoilless rifle]]\n|{{Flagu|United States}}\n|200<ref name=\"asiapacificdefencereporter.com\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mmmilitary.blogspot.com|title=Myanmar Defence Weapons|author=Mg Han|accessdate=29 November 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221112919/ht