strade/page/trade_register.php|title=SIPRI Trade Register|publisher=Stockholm Internationa+l Peace Research Institute|access-date=20 March 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414022558/http://armstrade.sipri.org/armstrade/page/trade_register.php#|archive-date=14 April 2010|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref> \n|| {{Flagu|India}}<br>{{flag|Soviet Union}}|| Acquired from India.\n|-\n|[[File:Type 62 tank - front.jpg|120px]]|| [[Type 62]]<ref name=\"rand.org\"/>|| [[Light tank]] || | 105<ref name=\"rand.org\"/> \n|| {{Flagu|China}} ||\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" | '''[[Armored car (military)|Armoured Vehicle]]'''\n|-\n| [[File:ChineseType85C2Veh.jpg|120px]]||[[Type 85 AFV|Type 85]] || Armoured personnel carrier || 250<ref name=\"armstrade.sipri.org\">{{cite web|url=http://armstrade.sipri.org/armstrade/page/trade_register.php|title=Trade Registers|accessdate=29 November 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414022558/http://armstrade.sipri.org/armstrade/page/trade_register.php#|archive-date=14 April 2010|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref> \n|| {{Flagu|China}}  || [[Type 85 AFV#Operators]]\n|-\n|[[File:Chinese Type 90 APC.jpg|120px]]|| [[Type 90 AFV]] || Armoured personnel carrier || 55<ref name=\"irrawaddy.org\"/> \n|| {{Flagu|China}} ||\n|-\n|[[File:Soviet MT-LB.JPEG|120px]]||[[MT-LB]]||Armoured personnel carrier|| 98<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sipri.org/contents/armstrad/at_data.html# |title=Archived copy |access-date=23 November 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107202457/http://www.sipri.org/contents/armstrad/at_data.html# |archive-date=7 November 2012 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n||{{Flagu|Ukraine}}<br>{{flag|Soviet Union}}||delivered in 2007. 3 regiments are equipped with 44 MT-LB MSh each.\n|-\n|[[File:BTR3.jpg|120px]]|| [[BTR-3]]U<ref>[[Amnesty International]], EU Office. [https://web.archive.org/web/20051219075837/http://www.amnesty-eu.org/static/documents/Final_Germa